column14:
Feel free to check out the **[Intro video](https://vimeo.com/110382358)** again. You can find the tour in the **Help** menu in the upper-right corner of Tracker..

      **What should I do next?**
      1. Tracker is collaborative, so **[invite your team](/projects/1942879/memberships)**.
      2. Write stories and prioritize those stories in the Backlog. Here's a video on **[how we write stories](https://vimeo.com/118871271)**.
      3. Learn more about the magic behind Tracker in our **[Quick Start Guide](/help/articles/quick_start/)**, including:
       * [Estimating story complexity](https://vimeo.com/118871742)
       * [Story workflow](https://vimeo.com/118871883)
       * [Velocity](https://vimeo.com/118872017) *(Velocity is why so many people love and rely on Tracker.)*
column21: Visit the Members section of the project and **[invite your team](/projects/1942879/memberships)**.
column23: Create stories and prioritize them in the Backlog.
